nuestras operaciones, nuestras iniciativas, maneras de trabajar y con todas las personas que hacen que todo esto sea posible \uD83D\uDCAA\uD83C\uDFFB</p><p>En este documento, vas a encontrar toda la informaci&oacute;n necesaria para empezar, incluyendo un panorama del proyecto, sus miembros, los procedimientos y procesos de gesti&oacute;n y desarrollo y tus primeros pasos en la organizaci&oacute;n. Por favor leelo detenidamente y no dudes en hacer preguntas siempre que lo necesites.</p><p>Bienvenido(a) a <em><strong>Bancard</strong></em> \uD83D\uDE0E.</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1089\" ac:original-width=\"1534\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"760\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"WhatsApp Image 2023-11-10 at 23.17.56.jpeg\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><hr /><p><em>Siguiente Paso</em> &rarr;</p><ac:link ac:card-appearance=\"block\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Presentaci&oacute;n General del Proyecto Bancard\" ri:version-at-save=\"10\" /><ac:link-body>Presentaci&oacute;n General del Proyecto Bancard</ac:link-body></ac:link><p> </p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2789474436"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":54},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2789474436/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2789474436/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2789474436/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2789474436/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2789474436","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2789474436/Bienvenido+a+a+Bancard","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2789474436","context":"/wiki